modName: Lady Isabella - 35 Nord - Vampire Brotherhood n Mage guild
summary: Female Nord 35, Vampire, Brotherhood Done + Mage Guild, MANY Side quests done, Only a few places unknown, Main quest First dragon with Delphine (Just after the Greybeards)
descriptionHtml:
Darkbrotherhood Master bed room, Filled with items, Check the chests.
Dragonbone/Plate, Glass, Thief, Darkbrotherhood, Ebony, and much much more!
The two barrels infront of Whiterun blacksmith, also filled with items. Mostly Leather and ingots (Material for Blacksmith) Also lots of Gems/Jewels, 

The character is Half done in many skills,
50+ Sneak, Onehanded, Speedcraft, Blacksmith, Destruction, Lightarmor, Lockpicking, Encharn, Heavyarmor, Marksman/Archery and \"Twohanded - Im not sure tbh (Think its 40+)\", Many other skills, 

Mainly this character would be fun playing because of all the Items i\'ve gathered, Most of the companions are also heavy geared, Especially Lydia (Full Deadra + Two Katana\'s) The Two onehanded weapons is a bug obvioursly, But its sweet!..
The rogue mage you can find south of Riften have my Archmage robe, (Greybeard robe looks amazing if you got that mod)
